Our Story

From A Simple Idea That's Changing Lives. One Wrap at a Time!

As a health and wellness specialist, healthy living has always been at the heart of my journey. Over 35 years ago, I was introduced to the concept of lymphatic body wraps, and I immediately recognized their transformative potential. From that moment, I knew I had to immerse myself in mastering this art, so I could share its benefits with others.

Throughout my years of working in rehabilitation centers, both locally and beyond, I’ve witnessed the remarkable impact these wraps can have. They don’t just aid in removing toxins from drug, nicotine, and alcohol use, but also help in flushing out excess fat cells. Lymphatic body wraps are a powerful tool in treating food, drug, and alcohol addictions, candida, autoimmune deficiencies, medication detox, weight loss, and so much more.

My mission has always been to support others in achieving their best health—regardless of age, condition, or circumstance. After years of refining and perfecting Bare Wraps, I’m excited to share this journey with you. Together, we can achieve transformative results and change your life for the better!

Our Best Services

At Bare Wraps, we offer personalized wellness services focused on detoxification, weight loss, and rejuvenation. Our signature lymphatic body wraps help eliminate toxins, reduce bloating, and target stubborn fat. Whether you're looking to detox, slim down, or simply relax, our expert team will tailor each treatment to your unique needs, helping you feel revitalized and balanced.

Ultimate Wraps

Bare Wraps Ultimate Body Wrap uses the highest grade essential oils on the market. The Bare Wraps Ultimate Body Wrap gives you the most effective inch-loss, purification ,detoxification and cellulite elimination possible in one sitting. This wrap assists in the process of toxin elimination and lymph flow through gentle pressure, increasing circulation as well as incorporating a heating element while you are wrapped. Detoxification and inch-loss are the primary goals of this wrap. With all of our wraps, we strive to build your immune system and remove accumulated waste. Your body will continue to eliminate toxins for the next 5 days post wrap.

Mineral Wraps

Bare Wraps Mineral Body Wrap is our signature inch loss wrap. This wrap works by using our own blend of specially formulated minerals that are designed to draw out impurities from your system, tone and tighten skin, detoxify, hydrate and replenish your body’s natural mineral supply which you may be lacking. We combine our minerals in a solution which will be applied at the start of your Bare Wrap as well as periodically throughout your wrap. Your body will continue to eliminate toxins for the next 24 hours post wrap.

Lymphatic Wraps

Our Lymphatic Body wrap is primarily a lymphatic drainage detoxification wrap. We apply our specially formulated detox cream and then contour the body using a plastic wrap. Our detox cream consists of a formula that helps stimulate the body's own natural lymphatic flow and elimination functions. This wrap assists in the process of waste elimination and lymphatic flow through gentle pressure and increasing circulation. This wrap is designed to help rid the body of toxic waste. Purification, cellulite elimination and inch-loss are the goals of this wrap. Your body will continue to eliminate toxins for the next 3 days post wrap.

Xtreme Wraps

Bare Wraps Xtreme Body Wrap is a two part process. We combine our Mineral Body Wrap as well as our Lymphatic Body Wrap in one 2 hour session. The Bare Wraps Extreme Body Wrap gives you incredibly effective inch-loss, purification, detoxification and elimination. This wrap assists in the process of toxin elimination and lymph flow through gentle pressure and increasing circulation. This wrap is designed to help rid the body of accumulated toxic waste. Detoxification and inch-loss are the primary goals of this wrap. Your body will continue to eliminate toxins for the next 3 days post wrap.

Body Sculpting Wraps

Our Body Sculpting Wraps are designed to contour and tone your body by targeting areas of stubborn fat and cellulite. Using natural ingredients, these wraps stimulate the lymphatic system to reduce water retention, smooth skin, and promote inch loss. Perfect for anyone looking to enhance their body shape while detoxifying, our Body Sculpting Wraps offer visible, lasting results with each session. Relax and let the wraps work deeply to rejuvenate and revitalize your body. Achieve a sculpted, confident look while supporting your wellness journey from the inside out. Book a free consultation to talk with one of our specialist

Lymphatic Massages

Our Lymphatic Massage services are crafted to stimulate the lymphatic system, aiding in detoxification, reducing inflammation, and boosting circulation. This gentle, therapeutic massage promotes the natural removal of toxins and excess fluids, leaving you feeling lighter and more energized. Ideal for anyone seeking improved immunity, reduced swelling, or enhanced wellness, each session offers deep relaxation and noticeable benefits. Experience a revitalized, balanced body as we help support your body’s natural healing processes, one massage at a time. Book a free consultation to talk with one of our specialist

Cellulite Treatments

Ideal for anyone seeking firmer, more even-looking skin, our cellulite wraps help rejuvenate problem areas and promote a more confident, sculpted look. Achieve noticeable results while relaxing in a comfortable, revitalizing treatment.

Lipo/Body Enhancements

Our Lipo and Body Enhancement services offer non-invasive solutions for contouring and refining your body’s natural shape. Using advanced techniques like Laser Lipo and Cavitation, we target stubborn fat cells, helping to reduce inches and sculpt areas such as the abdomen, thighs, and arms. Each session is designed to be comfortable and tailored to your goals.

Frequently Asked Question

What are lymphatic body wraps, and how do they work?

Lymphatic body wraps use natural ingredients to stimulate your lymphatic system, helping to remove toxins and excess fluids from the body. This process supports detoxification, reduces bloating, and targets stubborn fat cells, promoting weight loss and overall wellness.

What are some symptoms of needing To Detox?

Cellulite, lack of energy, overweight, mental confusion or fog, bowel disorders, allergies, dependencies on sugar, caffeine, alcohol, drugs etc., skin problems, body odor, excessive perspiration, headaches, digestive irregularity, candida overgrowth and exposure to environmental toxins and pollutants to name some.

How often should I get a Bare Wraps session?

For optimal results, we recommend starting with 1-2 sessions per week, depending on your goals. Regular sessions can help accelerate detoxification and weight loss, but our specialists will tailor a plan based on your unique needs.

Is Bare Wraps suitable for everyone?

Yes! Bare Wraps is designed to benefit individuals of all ages and conditions. Whether you’re detoxing, managing weight, or looking to support overall health, our wraps can be customized to meet your wellness needs.

When will I see results?

You will be able to see a noticeable difference within your first 1-3 wraps.  

What Should I wear?

Loose comfortable clothing. We provide disposable undergarments for each session.

What should I bring?

Just your self. However, many people bring music, their phones, or a book to enjoy as well.

How will I feel after my wrap?

You may feel a little tired and will want to rest or at least not exert an huge amount of energy for the next few hours. After a few hours we encourage you to take a walk or some other form of light exercise to help the process along. You also may want to shower however, we recommend you do not shower for 8 hours after your treatment. This allows the skin to really absorb all the minerals and/or creams we will have applied. Allowing you to benefit maximally from your wrap.

Is a wrap just temporary Water Loss?

No, absolutely not. In fact, we recommend drinking water to stay hydrated. Our wraps cleanse the lymphatic system and increase circulation which promotes fat loss as opposed to water loss.

What can I expect during a Bare Wraps session?

Each session lasts about an hour, where you’ll be wrapped in our specially formulated materials. You can relax while the wrap works to detoxify your body and promote fat reduction. Afterward, you may feel lighter, more energized, and refreshed!
